             was indicted for <rs id="t18190421-57-off326" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190421-57-off326" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190421-57-off326" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190421-57-cd327" type="crimeDate">19th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190421-57-off326 t18190421-57-cd327"></join>, from the person of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190421-57-victim702" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
                           Dudman
                        <interp inst="t18190421-57-victim702" type="surname" value="Dudman"></interp>
