                     </persName>
                     
                  , one pocketbook, value 1 s. 6 d., and one 1 l. bank note
            </rs>, his property.</p>
               <p>SECOND COUNT, the same, only stating the note to be the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190421-57-victim704" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Coventry
                  <interp inst="t18190421-57-victim704" type="surname" value="Coventry"></interp>
